Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.69,0:00:04.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,☆Dragon Ball Super☆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.61,0:00:14.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,曾经淡忘的梦想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.84,0:00:19.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如今再续前缘　又开始燃亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.52,0:00:24.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,给星星都连上线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.85,0:00:28.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就这样给宇宙画出了门框
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.44,0:00:34.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,跻身于全新的舞台上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.45,0:00:40.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,向诸神发出挑战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.62,0:00:42.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强烈☆猛烈☆活力满泻！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.66,0:00:45.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Let's Go！Go！恐慌奔走！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.17,0:00:49.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你输了就能变更强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.88,0:00:55.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不知天高地厚又何妨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.55,0:01:00.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,生无可悔　身无界限　一往无前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.51,0:01:02.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,壮烈☆激烈☆活力爆裂！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.64,0:01:05.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Let's Go！Yes！拳脚不绝！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.14,0:01:09.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,去沐浴颤抖的感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.90,0:01:13.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一个壮大传说　正在等着你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:27.81,0:01:30.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,被全王大人召唤来的孙悟空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.11,0:01:34.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不管周围人的担心，和全王愉快交谈了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.78,0:01:36.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,另一方面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.66,0:01:39.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,扎马斯和师父格瓦斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.28,0:01:41.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一起观察人类的未来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.12,0:01:45.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他对人类的野蛮生存方式失望透顶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.00,0:01:49.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,放任邪恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.84,0:01:52.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还称得上是神吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.96,0:01:54.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,然后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.42,0:01:57.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,特兰克斯终于回到未来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.80,0:02:01.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小舞应该倒在这里才对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.01,0:02:07.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,悟空他们能否拯救未来的地球呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.73,0:02:17.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,「再战黑悟空！超级赛亚人桃红登场」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.79,0:02:23.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,悟空先生！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.88,0:02:37.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可…可恶！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.26,0:02:41.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大家的敌人！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.30,0:02:43.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尝尝这个吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.72,0:02:43.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等下！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.52,0:02:46.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这个人不是「黑悟空」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.48,0:02:49.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊，是特兰克斯先生！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.69,0:02:51.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在芒果坡决战中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.02,0:02:54.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,让「黑悟空」吃了一击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.40,0:02:57.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太…太…太对不起了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.86,0:02:58.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,特兰克斯先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.07,0:03:01.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那个时候真是谢谢你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.87,0:03:03.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,特兰克斯先生！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.28,0:03:02.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,多亏了你我们抵抗军才…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.46,0:03:08.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,麻烦签个名！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.92,0:03:11.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你这家伙，这种时候还在想这些！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.75,0:03:13.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但…但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.42,0:03:15.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么但是不但是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.34,0:03:17.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也很想要他签名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.09,0:03:18.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过我忍住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.22,0:03:20.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么嘛，那一起找他要吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.65,0:03:32.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哎呀，没想到认错人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.73,0:03:35.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过这个人和「黑悟空」也太像了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.57,0:03:39.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那边那个人的面相也很凶恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.45,0:03:41.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,都是你的脸惹的祸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.16,0:03:43.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是你的脸惹祸了才对！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.20,0:03:44.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,才不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.91,0:03:47.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我的脸一点也不凶恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.08,0:03:47.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,「黑悟空」的脸才…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.91,0:03:49.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊，好了，好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.92,0:03:52.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,抵抗军的各位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.21,0:03:53.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,给你们介绍一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.42,0:03:55.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这两位是孙悟空先生和贝吉塔先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.42,0:03:58.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虽然说来话长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.72,0:04:01.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,和特兰克斯先生在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.26,0:04:02.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,应该是为了打到「黑悟空」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.47,0:04:05.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,特意从过去的世界来帮助我们的人吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.06,0:04:07.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是惊讶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.68,0:04:10.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,传闻中的帮手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.06,0:04:12.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是一个偏偏和「黑悟空」长得一样的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.35,0:04:15.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还有一个比「黑悟空」面相还要凶恶的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.44,0:04:17.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别再提面相了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.82,0:04:19.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么会这样？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.15,0:04:22.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,用时光机拯救世界的计划
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.20,0:04:25.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只有我，妈妈和小舞知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.29,0:04:32.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,难道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.79,0:04:36.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这件事你是从谁那里听说的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.59,0:04:38.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是…是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.09,0:04:40.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是小舞说的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.50,0:05:07.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小舞！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.92,0:05:19.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,特兰克斯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.13,0:05:24.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小舞！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.43,0:05:27.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,原来你平安无事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.68,0:05:30.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是我要说的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.22,0:05:31.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我很担心你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.60,0:05:35.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这也是我要说的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.32,0:05:43.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.07,0:05:46.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊，等…等等…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.32,0:05:47.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.41,0:05:51.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我一直以为你已经死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.83,0:05:58.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.17,0:06:02.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,男儿有泪不轻弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.05,0:06:07.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,欢迎回来，特兰克斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.14,0:06:08.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.81,0:06:21.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这里是新的据点吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.02,0:06:22.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.15,0:06:24.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,当我恢复意识
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.69,0:06:26.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,和反抗军会合以后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.82,0:06:29.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,以前的据点就受到了「黑悟空」的攻击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.83,0:06:34.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快点，往这边！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.51,0:06:49.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,开火！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.41,0:07:11.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要怕！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.91,0:07:15.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,特兰克斯他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.75,0:07:20.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,会从过去的世界带来援军
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.34,0:07:23.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.55,0:07:25.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.30,0:07:31.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,绝对不能放弃生存的希望！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.52,0:07:38.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.44,0:07:41.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是你守护了大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.73,0:07:42.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,「守护」？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.82,0:07:49.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,幸存下来的就这些人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.99,0:07:51.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就只有这些人吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.45,0:07:56.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我根本没能守护大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.58,0:07:59.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你已经全力以赴了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.54,0:08:01.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没什么可惭愧的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.13,0:08:03.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.17,0:08:11.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.51,0:08:14.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗨！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.59,0:08:49.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这就是你守护的笑容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.72,0:08:51.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,特兰克斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.55,0:08:57.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你不只面容，连说话也是个男子汉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.55,0:08:58.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.72,0:09:01.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小舞的朋友就是我们的朋友，对吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.64,0:09:03.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是，没错！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.48,0:09:05.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,来，坐这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.03,0:09:13.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们让点地方出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.36,0:09:16.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,少废话，快点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.07,0:09:18.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他想干什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.37,0:09:19.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,谁知道呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.50,0:09:30.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,爸爸！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.46,0:09:31.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别误会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.88,0:09:33.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是布玛给的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.63,0:09:38.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还剩下的两个里也放了不少东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.18,0:09:39.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,随便你们用吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.39,0:09:40.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好…好的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.60,0:09:43.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,布玛干得不错啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.68,0:09:45.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哼，那是当然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.35,0:09:46.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,毕竟是我的老婆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.98,0:09:50.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好，那我们就不客气了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.24,0:10:03.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你不会是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.96,0:10:07.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,弥次郎兵卫吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.58,0:10:08.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,孙？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.83,0:10:10.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,未来的你还活着啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.75,0:10:13.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你那个时候没死吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.26,0:10:16.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,您不是被人造人杀死了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.84,0:10:17.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.80,0:10:19.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,九死一生啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.43,0:10:22.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,加林仙人说了句「不用管我，你快吃」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.60,0:10:24.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就把最后的仙豆…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.14,0:10:29.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一想起这件事我就想哭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.07,0:10:35.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过，一向讨厌麻烦的弥次郎兵卫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.94,0:10:38.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,竟然和伙伴们在一起，真让我吃惊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.57,0:10:41.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一定是被加林仙人救的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.78,0:10:43.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,萌生了战斗的决心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.74,0:10:44.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过这家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.04,0:10:47.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,战斗时总是不知道躲在哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.50,0:10:49.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只有吃饭的时候才出现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.92,0:10:52.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我说你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.21,0:10:55.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在说这些干什么！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.13,0:10:56.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为事实就是如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.88,0:10:59.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这种事就别计较了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.60,0:11:05.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好久没有看到大家这样的表情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.97,0:11:07.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的谢谢你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.89,0:11:09.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在道谢还太早了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.48,0:11:11.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等我们打倒了「黑悟空」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.98,0:11:14.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,恢复真正的和平的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.99,0:11:18.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你也要战斗吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.07,0:11:19.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.57,0:11:21.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他是来观战的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.70,0:11:23.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,「黑悟空」让我一个人解决
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.62,0:11:25.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啥，也算我一份啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.20,0:11:28.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不，这次轮到我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.71,0:11:30.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那么，猜拳决定吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.50,0:11:31.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.50,0:11:32.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,石头剪刀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.71,0:11:34.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,说了不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.84,0:11:35.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,先是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.01,0:11:36.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不干！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.51,0:11:38.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好像没什么紧张感了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.05,0:11:40.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你不出就算你输啊，石头剪刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.01,0:11:40.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,布！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.55,0:11:42.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我输了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.01,0:11:45.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你那只软弱的手怎么赢得了我！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.89,0:11:46.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,爸爸！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.60,0:11:49.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,让我也加入战斗吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.77,0:11:51.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这里是我生活的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.85,0:11:53.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是我们生活的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.73,0:11:55.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以请让我亲手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.69,0:11:56.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.57,0:11:57.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,爸爸！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.65,0:11:59.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你不是还有那位姑娘吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.95,0:12:02.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,万一情况不妙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.70,0:12:06.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,起码你们还可以回到过去的世界，明白吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.70,0:12:10.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那家伙会说这样的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.33,0:12:11.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他也成长了不少是吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.96,0:12:13.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不，其…其实
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.92,0:12:15.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们不是那种关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.76,0:12:21.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好了！我们走吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.01,0:12:27.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大家不要输啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.24,0:12:48.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,多么悲凉的景象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.41,0:12:51.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是我能看到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.33,0:12:55.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是从人类这些害虫中解放出来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.13,0:12:58.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这片大地的美丽光辉的未来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.01,0:13:03.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还有一点就可以完成这理想家园了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.55,0:13:06.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,人类啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.09,0:13:08.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等待接受制裁的那一刻吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.11,0:13:16.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.02,0:13:20.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这样无论他在哪里都可以找到我们了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.20,0:13:28.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,来了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.42,0:13:38.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,「黑悟空」！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.75,0:13:41.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我明明破坏了时光机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.63,0:13:44.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,告诉你一件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.88,0:13:47.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,将要葬送你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.01,0:13:50.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是我超级赛亚人蓝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.77,0:13:53.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.81,0:13:55.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,见到超级赛亚人蓝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.81,0:13:57.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,竟然面不改色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.27,0:14:00.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就好像他曾经见过一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.99,0:14:04.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是绝妙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.82,0:14:09.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这就是被神的气息环绕的战斗民族形态啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.08,0:14:13.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,锻炼得不错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.12,0:14:16.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过毕竟是人类
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.00,0:14:20.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他什么时候到我眼前的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.25,0:14:22.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这家伙比以前和卡卡罗特战斗时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.80,0:14:24.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,力量又提升了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.13,0:14:28.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.55,0:14:32.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在超级赛亚人蓝面前是没用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.69,0:14:42.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看到和自己长得一样的人被打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.69,0:14:44.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,心情真复杂啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.78,0:14:48.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我终于明白在波特夫星时贝吉塔的心情了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.70,0:14:49.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,悟空先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.16,0:14:51.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,「毕竟是人类」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.08,0:14:53.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这种口吻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.20,0:14:56.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,「黑悟空」的真实身份果然是那个神 扎马斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.79,0:15:00.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,难道真的是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.02,0:15:21.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这种感觉是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.54,0:15:40.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,爸爸！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.71,0:15:50.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,人类的身体能做到这个地步很不错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.01,0:15:53.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,作为奖励，让你们见识一下好东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.64,0:15:54.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.28,0:16:09.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,发生什么事了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.37,0:16:20.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.83,0:16:29.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,「黑悟空」的颜色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.02,0:16:45.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如何，这个颜色很美吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.81,0:16:49.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,以你们的品味命名的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.86,0:16:50.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,桃红
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.61,0:16:55.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不错，超级赛亚人桃红
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.24,0:16:59.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,超级赛亚人桃红
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.04,0:17:09.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我终于将孙悟空的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.92,0:17:12.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,完全地化为己有了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.76,0:17:17.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,孙悟空，你应该高兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.80,0:17:22.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你因为我而到达美丽的至高点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.02,0:17:26.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你说的什么我完全听不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.19,0:17:29.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,毕竟是肉眼凡胎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.98,0:17:32.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,理解不了我的圣言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.36,0:17:34.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我的高贵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.32,0:17:38.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还有我的志向和美丽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.08,0:17:42.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对，我的存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.08,0:17:46.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,完全是孤高的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.46,0:17:49.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那家伙果然挺恶心的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.71,0:17:51.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,「黑悟空」！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.84,0:17:54.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你在和谁说话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.09,0:17:55.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你的对手是我！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.59,0:17:57.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还不明白吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.30,0:18:01.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,已经没你出场的份了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.10,0:18:02.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你说什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.27,0:18:05.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你该懂得引退，前戏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.69,0:18:09.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不知死活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.15,0:18:11.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,爸爸！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.96,0:18:29.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,让你粉身碎骨！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.26,0:18:43.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什…什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.23,0:18:49.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,刚刚叫你前戏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.48,0:18:50.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,应该修正一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.36,0:18:52.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,前菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.15,0:18:57.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,贝吉塔，你是一道美味的前菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.99,0:19:00.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,混…混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.54,0:19:10.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,爸爸！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.21,0:19:13.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,正因为你这道前菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.75,0:19:16.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我又变强了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.21,0:19:19.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那么，为了征服主菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.18,0:19:22.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,向更高的层次挖掘吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.56,0:19:24.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.72,0:19:25.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,让我来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.97,0:19:27.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,悟空先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.48,0:19:34.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,悟空先生的超级赛亚人蓝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.36,0:19:36.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,悟空先生他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.61,0:19:38.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一开始就要使出全力吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.61,0:19:40.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,特兰克斯，贝吉塔就拜托你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.78,0:19:41.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是…是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.83,0:19:46.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你之前所说的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.87,0:19:48.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,痛苦让我变得更强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.62,0:19:50.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是这个意思啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.17,0:19:53.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我现在所在的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.79,0:19:55.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是一个肉眼凡胎无法到达的境界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.17,0:20:00.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你也想尝尝这样的力量吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.26,0:20:02.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯，也许吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.98,0:20:09.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,爸爸！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.85,0:20:11.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,爸爸！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.40,0:20:19.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,势均力敌？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.99,0:20:21.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不，不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.12,0:20:31.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.13,0:20:43.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是龟派气功？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.59,0:20:46.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.02,0:20:52.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不许你再继续任性而为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.24,0:21:02.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,扎马斯大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.99,0:21:05.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,扎马斯，那家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.71,0:21:15.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,「黑悟空」和扎马斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.79,0:21:18.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不是同一个人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.88,0:21:20.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们约定好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.09,0:21:23.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,孙悟空的命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.51,0:21:26.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,由我来解决
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.81,0:21:38.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,咻咻咻　咻咻一瞬间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.19,0:21:40.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,触碰在眉宇间的指尖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.73,0:21:43.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,噔噔噔　头发已冲冠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.28,0:21:45.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,力量注满　这就是赛亚人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.86,0:21:49.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要迸发光芒的Shining Heart
